org.quackbot.dao.model

Interface ChannelEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericEntry

    public interface ChannelEntry
extends GenericEntry
    Bean that holds all known Channel information. This is meant to be integrated with JPersist and the database. Only configure if going to add to database, otherwise let JPersist configure it.

    If this needs to be changed in database, call #updateDB()

    Author:
    Leon Blakey
